### =================================================================
### DISHES API - PRUEBAS COMPLETAS
### =================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### 1. GET - Listar todos los platos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/generic/dishes/

### 2. GET - Ver plato específico
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/generic/dishes/1/

### 3. POST - Crear plato (necesitas tener una categoría creada primero)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/generic/dishes/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pizza Margherita",
    "description": "Pizza clásica con tomate, mozzarella y albahaca fresca",
    "price": "25000.00",
    "category": 1,
    "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 4. POST - Crear hamburguesa
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/generic/dishes/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Hamburguesa Clásica",
    "description": "Hamburguesa de carne con queso, lechuga, tomate y salsas",
    "price": "18000.00",
    "category": 2,
    "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 5. PUT - Actualizar plato completo
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/generic/dishes/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Pizza Margherita Premium",
    "description": "Pizza gourmet con mozzarella de búfala",
    "price": "32000.00",
    "category": 1,
    "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### 6. PATCH - Actualización parcial (solo precio)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/generic/dishes/1/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": "28000.00"
}

### 7. DELETE - Eliminar plato
# DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/generic/dishes/1/